<p>Testing methodology includes clock injection for time-sensitive tests (invite TTL, key expiry), concurrent goroutine stress tests (up to 10 workers), mock HTTP servers for external systems (Splunk HEC, OIDC JWKS, CEF/Syslog), and full registry restart round-trips for persistence verification.</p>

